  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00001",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "安禄山上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "花色盈盈千般好，唐室文武贺圣朝。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "俺，节度使安禄山是也。适才宫中谢宴而出，行来金马门，待俺加鞭过。且住，我想金马门，乃是文官出入之所。我如何行走得呢？哎，想我既拜贵妃娘娘为母，天子宠爱，满朝文武，谁不钦敬，谅他们不敢轻慢与我也。",
      "text_length": 97
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "勒马停蹄闯禁门，上尊天子压群臣。一人中了万岁意，扬鞭闯过金马门。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "安禄山下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李白、贺知章同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "携手相扶漫遣怀，散步逍遥过大街。长安多少富贵客，谁似我好酒不贪财。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "圣上有道众群僚，万马营中爵位高。七篇锦绣真贵宝，笔尖犹如斩将刀。耳边又听得銮铃啸，腾起烟尘渐渐高。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "老年兄你可曾看见么？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "看见什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "金马门内，一个乘骑行走，是我们翰林院学士哪家的朋友，真正可笑。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "何笑之有？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "可笑吓可笑。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "是文官出入就下轿，不该马上逞英豪。一言未尽顷刻到，一见奴才气怎消。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "哎，我道是谁，原来是他。老年兄，我想节度使乃甚等之人，他也走起金马门来了！你我坐在此间，看他怎样过去？",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "说得有理。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李白、贺知章同坐。安禄山暗上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "可恼吓可恼。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "不生烦恼惹烦恼，酒鬼无礼犯人嘲。自夸腹内文章妙，轻慢天子压群僚。能屈能伸真君子，不知风色小儿曹。假陪笑险将他告，想必是学士醉醇醪。",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "吓，众位学士公，请来见礼。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "我道是谁，原来是节度使，请见一礼。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "唔，大胆可恶，岂有此理。我想金马门，乃是先帝太祖所立，是我们翰林院学士出入的道路。你是甚等之人，也敢行走。真乃无礼。我等坐在此间，看你怎样过去。",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "吓，学士公，这就是你的不是了。俺也曾南征北剿，挣下汗马功劳。况俺既拜贵妃娘娘为母，你竟敢慢待与我，真乃可恼。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "节度使，我且问你，方才你说你既拜贵妃娘娘为母。她乃一朝国母，岂容你膝下如此无礼。你道是南征北剿，挣下汗马功劳，你有何功劳，不过是圣上宠爱与你，老爷平素皆知。你可晓得我醉写吓蛮之事么？",
      "text_length": 91
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "倒也不知。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "你且听者。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "金马门怒恼了翰林院，酒醉辱骂安禄山。下国夷蛮把兵变，扰乱吾主心不安。传旨曾将下官宣，那时酒醉把君参。杨国忠双手捧过砚，高力士脱靴在金殿。我也曾斗酒将诗献，虽然沉醉写吓蛮。若不是番邦降表献，削尔的首级挂高杆。",
      "text_length": 103
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "岂有此理。想我醉写吓蛮之时，杨国忠捧砚，高力士脱靴。圣上亲自御手调羹，若非念你在朝奉君，我把你这大胆的奴才，送至君前，削尔的首级。哎，节度使，学生酒醉失言，得罪了。",
      "text_length": 82
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "唗！大胆可恶，我看你怎样过去！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "学士公，莫怪我说，近日朝廷之事，都被你们这些文官，颠倒坏尽。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "哎，节度使，这就是你的不是了。你骂众位学士，李学士在此着恼，老夫与你宛转周旋，说了许多的好话，你反而说朝中之事，被我们文官坏尽。想昔日愧阳领兵，大战丘山，逼反贾同，围困在内，内无粮草，外无救兵。那时仰面朝天，叹曰：自己能有几乎为狗，何况与你，你可知作狗奉君无日乎。哎，真乃无理。",
      "text_length": 139
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "哎，年兄不必动怒，他能读了几句诗书，犹如对牛弹琴一般。待我问他几句。哎，节度使，你说道朝中之事，被我文官坏尽。你有何能，你的来历，还当我等不知。",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "尔等知晓甚么？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "你且听了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "你生来油头白粉面，肥嫩身体软如棉。蛮夷无宝将你献，谄媚邀宠不羞惭。虽然未曾对宫院，赛过嫔妃一样般。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "哼。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "真乃大胆。人来！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "书童甲、书童乙同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲",
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "来了，老爷有何吩咐？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "命你二人，叫骂安禄山，哪个骂得入耳者，回府有赏。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲",
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "赏什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "每人赏酒一坛，若骂得不好，重责二十大板。只管前去叫骂。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲"
      ],
      "text": "哦伙计，老爷教我们叫骂节度使，你我如何敢骂呢？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "呔，安禄山！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00047",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "唗，大胆的狗才！你乃甚等之人，擅敢毁骂节度使，记打记责，还不与我退下！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00048",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲",
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00049",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "节度使，请息怒，常言道得好，家主犯事，尽出门下之人，学生这厢陪罪了，莫要与他一般见识。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00050",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安禄山"
      ],
      "text": "哼。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00051",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "啊大胆可恶，你还不如我门下之人呢。来，",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00052",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲",
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00053",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "只管放大胆地叫骂！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00054",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲",
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00055",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲"
      ],
      "text": "呔安禄山，我的儿吓。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00056",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "呔安禄山，我的孙子吓！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00057",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲"
      ],
      "text": "你骂长了一辈咧。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00058",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "下不为例。哎，安禄山，你且听了！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00059",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "安家小子真标标致，无耻无羞，甚么东西。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00060",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲"
      ],
      "text": "你骂得不好，待我去骂。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00061",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童乙"
      ],
      "text": "让你去骂。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00062",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲"
      ],
      "text": "啊，安禄山，我的舅子吓。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00063",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "书童甲"
      ],
      "text": "安家小子真可耻，把你进贡似妾姬。弥子之下藏食子，你与他同德一般齐。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00064",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "老年兄。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00065",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "学士公。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00066",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李白"
      ],
      "text": "非是学生夸口，慢道我李白的诗书，就是我的仆人，他也知道弥子藏食子之事。老年兄这一节，你可知道否？",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006059_e00067",
      "play_id": "02006059",
      "scene_id": "02006059_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺知章"
      ],
      "text": "倒也不知。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
